high_descs: Go across the room to the sink.
Pick up the chef's knife in front of the sink and on the left.
Go to the island past the stove on the right.
Slice the apple on the island.
Take the chef knife to the recycle bin.
Put the knife in the recycle bin.
Turn around and go back to the island.
Pick up a piece of the apple.
Go past the sink to the microwave on the left of the fridge.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave.
Take the hot apple slice to the recycle bin.
Put the apple slice in the recycle bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple slice in the recycle bin.

high_descs: Turn left walk forward then head to the sink
Pick up the first knife in front of the sink
Turn left move forward then turn left make a step then face the table
Slice the apple on the table
Turn left and face the trash bin
Put the knife in the trash bin
Turn left then head to the table
Pick up a slice of apple
Turn left then head to the microwave
Put in and out the slice apple in the microwave
Turn right and head to the trash bin
Put the slice apple in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the warm  slice apple in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn around and cross the kitchen to the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter that's closest to you.
Turn left and walk towards the stove, then head left again until the kitchen island is on your left and turn to face it.
Use the knife to slice the apple by the loaf of bread.
Turn around to face the green trash bin next to the stove.
Place the knife in the trash bin.
Turn back around to face the sliced apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the island.
Turn left and once the counter blocks you, turn right and move to the microwave.
Place the apple slice inside the microwave and then remove once heated.
Turn left and move to the stove, then take another left to move to the other side of the stove, facing the green trash bin again.
Place the apple slice in the green trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a heated slice of apple.
